{
	"nodes":[
		{
			"id":"agentops-center",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"AgentOps\n让 AI 编程助手从一次性会话，变成可积累、可验证、可闭环的工程系统",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":40,
			"y":20,
			"width":340,
			"height":120
		},
		{
			"id":"agentops-git",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"Git 工作流基础\nIssue → Branch → Commit → Push → CI → PR → Merge\nAgentOps 借用这套工程节奏来管理 AI 协作",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-520,
			"y":-80,
			"width":320,
			"height":140
		},
		{
			"id":"agentops-git-detail",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"关键点\n- 不在 main 直接改\n- 小步 commit 方便回滚\n- PR/CI 负责质量闸门\n- Worktree 支持并行开发",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-520,
			"y":100,
			"width":320,
			"height":180
		},
		{
			"id":"agentops-value",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"问题与价值\nAI 会失忆、会重复踩坑、也容易在没有验证时贸然提交",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":40,
			"y":-240,
			"width":320,
			"height":120
		},
		{
			"id":"agentops-value-detail",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"三大缺口\n1. 判断力验证缺失\n2. 知识不能积累\n3. 工作循环没有闭合\n\n对应：/vibe、.agents/、/post-mortem + /forge",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":400,
			"y":-240,
			"width":340,
			"height":160
		},
		{
			"id":"agentops-skills",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"Skills 系统\n把复杂流程封装成带契约的命令，让 Claude 按固定流程执行",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":600,
			"y":-40,
			"width":320,
			"height":120
		},
		{
			"id":"agentops-skills-detail",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"探索 / 执行 / 验证\n- /plan /research\n- /implement /crank /rpi\n- /vibe /council /post-mortem /forge\n\n本质：SKILL.md 定义输入、输出、步骤",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":600,
			"y":120,
			"width":340,
			"height":180
		},
		{
			"id":"agentops-hooks",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"Hooks 机制\n在会话与 Git 的关键事件上自动执行检查、注入知识、阻止危险操作",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":980,
			"y":-40,
			"width":320,
			"height":120
		},
		{
			"id":"agentops-hooks-detail",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"两层 Hook\n- Claude 运行时 Hooks：SessionStart / PreToolUse / SessionEnd ...\n- Git Hooks：commit / push 前后\n\n重点：PreToolUse 做风险门禁与分支保护",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":980,
			"y":120,
			"width":360,
			"height":180
		},
		{
			"id":"agentops-flywheel",
			"type":"text",
			"text":".agents/ 知识飞轮\n把经验、目标、发现、背景和产出沉淀进项目环境，而不是留在会话里",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":20,
			"y":360,
			"width":340,
			"height":120
		},
		{
			"id":"agentops-flywheel-detail",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"飞轮路径\nao lookup 检索相关知识 → Claude 执行 → /post-mortem 总结 → /forge 写入 .agents/ → 下次会话继续注入",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":400,
			"y":360,
			"width":360,
			"height":160
		},
		{
			"id":"agentops-loop",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"完整工作流闭环\n计划 → 实现 → 验证 → PR Review → 合并 → 复盘 → 知识沉淀 → 下次更强",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-520,
			"y":360,
			"width":340,
			"height":120
		},
		{
			"id":"agentops-loop-detail",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"一条主线\n/plan 生成 Issue\n→ /implement 或 /crank\n→ /vibe\n→ push + CI\n→ /council\n→ merge main\n→ /post-mortem + /forge",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-520,
			"y":520,
			"width":340,
			"height":180
		},
		{
			"id":"agentops-source",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"[[AgentOps-学习笔记]]",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":860,
			"y":420,
			"width":260,
			"height":80
		}
	],
	"edges":[
		{"id":"edge-center-git","fromNode":"agentops-center","fromSide":"left","toNode":"agentops-git","toSide":"right"},
		{"id":"edge-center-value","fromNode":"agentops-center","fromSide":"top","toNode":"agentops-value","toSide":"bottom"},
		{"id":"edge-center-skills","fromNode":"agentops-center","fromSide":"right","toNode":"agentops-skills","toSide":"left"},
